---
import ProfileIdentity from '../components/ProfileIdentity.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config/site';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="关于许汝林"
  description="许汝林是一名拥有 7 年开发经验的产品型全栈工程师，擅长从需求到上线交付复杂产品。"
>
  <div class="container about-page" data-pagefind-body>
    <header>
      <p class="eyebrow">ABOUT XU RULIN</p>
      <h1>我不只写代码，也负责让产品落地。</h1>
      <p>{siteConfig.author.bio}</p>
    </header>

    <ProfileIdentity variant="full" />

    <div class="profile-facts" aria-label="个人简介">
      <div>
        <strong>{siteConfig.author.age}</strong>
        <span>当前年龄</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>{siteConfig.author.experienceYears} 年</strong>
        <span>开发经验</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>全栈</strong>
        <span>交付边界</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <section>
        <span>01</span>
        <h2>从需求到交付</h2>
        <p>把模糊需求拆成可实现方案，完成系统设计、前后端开发、数据建模、部署和持续迭代。</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <span>02</span>
        <h2>解决复杂业务</h2>
        <p>擅长交易流程、运营后台、RBAC 权限、审计日志、异步任务、大数据导出和分表等场景。</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <span>03</span>
        <h2>技术与产品并重</h2>
        <p>使用 PHP/Laravel、Go、Vue 3/TypeScript、MySQL、Redis、RabbitMQ、ClickHouse 与对象存储完成可靠交付。</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-note">
      <p class="eyebrow">BUILD · WRITE · CONNECT</p>
      <h2>有产品想法，或者复杂问题，可以聊聊。</h2>
      <p>欢迎讨论产品、系统设计和工程实践，也欢迎指出文章中的错误。</p>
      <a class="button button--primary" href="/guestbook/">前往留言板 →</a>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page { padding-block: clamp(72px, 10vw, 130px) 120px; }
  header { max-width: 900px; }
  header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.2rem); line-height: 1.02; }
  header > p:last-child { max-width: 620px; margin: 20px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .about-page > :global([data-profile-identity]) { margin-top: 36px; }
  .profile-facts { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); margin-top: 72px; border-block: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .profile-facts > div { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; padding: 26px 24px; }
  .profile-facts > div + div { border-left: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .profile-facts strong { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.7rem); line-height: 1; }
  .profile-facts span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 18px; margin-top: 72px; }
  .about-grid section { padding: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .about-grid span { color: var(--accent-strong); font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.72rem; }
  .about-grid h2 { margin: 44px 0 12px; font-size: 1.35rem; }
  .about-grid p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); }
  .about-note { margin-top: 100px; padding: clamp(28px, 7vw, 74px); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); color: var(--canvas); background: var(--ink); }
  .about-note h2 { max-width: 700px; margin: 0; font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5rem); line-height: 1; }
  .about-note > p:not(.eyebrow) { color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--canvas) 70%, transparent); }
  .about-note .button { margin-top: 22px; color: var(--ink); background: var(--canvas); }
  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .profile-facts > div { padding-inline: 14px; }
  }
</style>

